Body: Had the same issue. Make sure that you have started /analytics/bin/wso2server.sh and /broker/bin/wso2.sh.
Can i ask you more questions?
You are right. We assumed previous emm can be run normally without DAS(analytics) support so we did not run analytics base on IoT3.0, but we were wrong. Now it work, thank you very much.

WSO2 IoT 3.1.0 is released and it has included a script to change the host name to IP. Default server comes with localhost URL configurations and an SSL certificate with localhost common name. Therefore if you need to change localhost to an IP
column9:
please run the change-ip.sh script in [WSO2 IoT 3.1.0]/scripts folder.

"
